{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"body":"SCENARIO 1 (parallel siblings) PASS live — R1/R4 core. Two independent story changes off feature/e2e-20260704: change 251 (sibling A, https://rebar.solutions.navateam.com/c/rebar/+/251) + change 252 (sibling B, https://rebar.solutions.navateam.com/c/rebar/+/252). BOTH earned LLM-Review+1 (rebar review bot) AND Verified+1 (rebar CI bot; CI dispatched on the feature branch by g2p — webhook + branch-agnostic dispatch live-proven; wall-clock ~830-849s). Submitted A then B: feature-branch history shows A landed (4159e8be3), then B landed via a Gerrit-created MERGE COMMIT c0acd6091 'Merge sibling story B into feature/e2e-20260704' — MERGE_IF_NECESSARY submit strategy, ZERO manual rebase, ZERO vote wipe (R4: no invalidation fragility). CI wall-clock ~14min/run."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783125820763510001,"uuid":"24a20ef7-aead-4f43-8681-d0d6e2db035b"}